The paper discusses the authentication protocol for wireless sensor networks, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The integration of WSNs with IoT also brings forth stricter security requirements, which can fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
